---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro"
import Footer from "../../layouts/Footer.astro"
import '@fontsource/playfair-display';
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import interes1 from "../../assets/interes1.png"
import interes2 from "../../assets/interes2.png"
import interes3 from "../../assets/interes3.png"
import interes4 from "../../assets/interes4.png"
import interes5 from "../../assets/interes5.png"
import interes6 from "../../assets/interes6.png"
---

<Layout title="Interés Cultural - FMEW">
    <div class="my-20 md:mt-0 mx-10 lg:mx-0">
        <h1 class="text-center font text-4xl">La Legislatura porteña declara de interés cultural a la Fundación María Elena Walsh</h1>
        <div class="md:max-w-6xl m-auto my-8 lg:px-0">
            <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/FiQYMJNAdeY" class="mt-4 m-auto md:w-3/4 md:h-96" title="Distinción a la Fundación María Elena Walsh" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-5 mt-4">
                <Image src={interes1} alt="interes1" class="w-full md:w-96"/>
                <Image src={interes2} alt="interes2" class="w-96"/>
                <Image src={interes3} alt="interes3" class="w-96"/>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-5 mt-4">
                <Image src={interes4} alt="interes4" class="w-96"/>
                <Image src={interes5} alt="interes5" class="w-96"/>
                <Image src={interes6} alt="interes6" class="w-96"/>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-4"><b>Agradecemos el reconocimiento que nos han otorgado por nuestro trabajo en la difusión de la obra de María Elena Walsh para las nuevas generaciones.</b></p>
            <p class="mt-4"><a class="underline" target="_blank" href="https://www.instagram.com/bacultura/">Ministerio de Cultura BA</a> , <a target="_blank" class="underline" href="https://www.instagram.com/sanmihanovich/">Sandra Mihanovich</a> y <a target="_blank" class="underline" href="https://www.instagram.com/roycortinaok/">Roy Cortina</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <Footer/>
</Layout>
<style>
    .font{
        font-family: "playfair display", sans-serif;
    }
    li{
        font-weight: 300 !important;
    }
</style>